---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy" description="SafetyTAP privacy policy. How we handle your data and protect your information.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy tracking-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-dark/50 mt-2">Last updated: February 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-dark/80 leading-relaxed">
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-navy">What SafetyTAP Collects</h2>
      <p>When you use the SafetyTAP Telegram bot, we process the photos and text messages you send in order to generate a response. We do not store the content of your messages, photos, or the responses generated. Each interaction is processed and discarded.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-navy">What We Log</h2>
      <p>We log minimal interaction metadata for monitoring and improving the service: whether a message included a photo, whether it included text, response time, and any errors. We do not log message content, photos, or response text. We do not log personally identifiable information.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-navy">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>SafetyTAP uses Telegram for message delivery and Anthropic's Claude API for generating responses. Your messages are transmitted to these services as part of normal operation. Please review <a href="https://telegram.org/privacy" class="text-teal hover:text-teal-light underline-offset-2 hover:underline transition-colors">Telegram's privacy policy</a> and <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/privacy" class="text-teal hover:text-teal-light underline-offset-2 hover:underline transition-colors">Anthropic's privacy policy</a> for their data handling practices.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-navy">Website Analytics</h2>
      <p>This website uses privacy-friendly analytics that do not use cookies and do not track individual visitors. We collect aggregate page view data to understand how the site is used.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-navy">Contact Form</h2>
      <p>If you submit the contact form, we collect the information you provide (name, email, company, message) solely for the purpose of responding to your inquiry. We do not share this information with third parties.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-navy">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this policy? <a href="/contact" class="text-teal hover:text-teal-light underline-offset-2 hover:underline transition-colors">Get in touch</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
